Bug.WithStack:
Build id: 200302211557
When defining an external program you can use vars like: ${workspace_loc:/MyProject}
You should be able to do the same in the refresh tab too. Deferred post 2.1 As of now 'LATER' and 'REMIND' resolutions are no longer supported. Please reopen this bug if it is still valid for you.

