*** Bug 32779 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***
Fixed. The manager was iterating over a keySet() and removing elements from the 
table. Thus, the keySet could be modified as elements are removed from the 
table (according to the spec for Map.keySet()). Changed to use a copy of the 
keySet.
Please verify, Luc.

